wikibaselexeme-api-error-parameter-requi: API error message that is being reported when parameter is missing.
wikibaselexeme-api-error-parameter-inval: API error message that is being reported when provided data parameter is not a valid JSON
wikibaselexeme-api-error-lexeme-not-foun:
API error message that is being reported when Lexeme with provided ID does not exist.

Parameters:
* $1 - ID of the Lexeme
wikibaselexeme-api-error-form-not-found:
API error message that is being reported when Form with provided ID does not exist.

Parameters:
* $1 - ID of the Form
wikibaselexeme-api-error-json-field-requ:
API error message that is being reported when required field in JSON object is not present. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Name of the parameter that is expected to be JSON object. 
* $2 - Path of the field inside of the JSON object (e.g "array-field-name/0/other-field-name")
wikibaselexeme-api-error-json-field-not-:
API error message that is being reported when field in JSON object expected to contain serialized Item ID, but contains something else. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Name of the parameter that is expected to be JSON object.
* $2 - Path of the field inside of the JSON object (e.g "array-field-name/0/other-field-name")
* $3 - Provided value
wikibaselexeme-api-error-json-field-has-:
API error message that is being reported when field in JSON object expected to be of certain type, but value of another type was provided. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Name of the parameter that is expected to be JSON object.
* $2 - Path of the field inside of the JSON object (e.g "array-field-name/0/other-field-name")
* $3 - Expected type name (e.g. string, array, object) 
* $4 - Provided value type name
wikibaselexeme-api-error-parameter-not-l:
API error message that is being reported when parameter is expected to contain serialized Lexeme ID, but contains something else. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Name of the parameter
* $2 - Provided value
wikibaselexeme-api-error-parameter-not-f:
API error message that is being reported when parameter is expected to contain serialized Form ID, but contains something else. 

Parameters:
* $1 - Name of the parameter
* $2 - Provided value
wikibaselexeme-api-error-representation-: API error message that is being reported when one of provided representations is empty
API error message that is being reported when one of provided representations' language is empty

API error message that is being reported when provided representation language is inconsistent.

Parameters:
* $1 - Expected language
* $2 - Given language
wikibaselexeme-api-error-form-must-have-: API error message that is being reported when no representations were provided
wikibaselexeme-api-error-representations:
API error message that is being reported when at least one of the provided representations reuses the language

Parameters:
* $1 - Laguage that was reused
